ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - SIGNATURE Jersey FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION RELATING TO TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of Jersey, under entrustment from the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland, FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION RELATING TO TAX MATTERS.
